<help communications tell>

Attempts to tell a message to some other person.  The person can be
anywhere, as long as they are visible to you.  You cannot 'tell' NPC's
anything at this time.

syntax:  tell <<target_person> <<message text>

example:  tell gideon I have your bible!
<color = red>
See Also:  say, osay, channels, discuss, emote, reply
</color></help>

